data.value:
Buongiorno! (that's "Hello!" in Italian)
This installer will help you patch your existing UNDERTALE copy to include Undertale Together mod.
What you'll need: 1) A legitimate copy of UNDERTALE v1.08 (plz no piracy) 1.1) Anything lower than v1.08 (or 2.0.0.2 on GOG) won't work! 2) A little bit of patience. 3) dog.
